---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'

const lastUpdated = 'January 25, 2025'
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | Aloha Media Studio"
  description="Terms of Service for Aloha Media Studio. Please read these terms carefully before using our services."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-[var(--color-void)]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-stone)] mb-12">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            By accessing or using the Aloha Media Studio website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our website or services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Our Services</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            Aloha Media Studio provides video production, photography, branding, web design, audio production, and podcast services. Specific terms for individual projects will be outlined in separate project agreements or contracts.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Project Agreements</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Before beginning any project, we will provide a detailed proposal or contract outlining:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--color-mist)] space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Scope of work and deliverables</li>
            <li>Timeline and milestones</li>
            <li>Pricing and payment terms</li>
            <li>Revision policies</li>
            <li>Ownership and usage rights</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
            Project-specific agreements will supplement these general Terms of Service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Payments</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Payment terms will be specified in your project agreement. Generally:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--color-mist)] space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>A deposit may be required before work begins</li>
            <li>Final payment is due upon project completion or as specified</li>
            <li>Late payments may result in work delays or additional fees</li>
            <li>All prices are in US dollars unless otherwise stated</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-cream)]">Your Content:</strong> You retain ownership of all content, materials, and assets you provide to us for use in your project.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-cream)]">Our Work:</strong> Upon full payment, you will receive the rights to use the final deliverables as specified in your project agreement. We may retain the right to display completed work in our portfolio unless otherwise agreed.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-cream)]">Third-Party Content:</strong> Any third-party content (stock photos, music, fonts, etc.) used in your project may be subject to separate licensing terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Client Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            As a client, you agree to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--color-mist)] space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Provide accurate information and materials needed for your project</li>
            <li>Respond to communications and requests in a timely manner</li>
            <li>Provide feedback within agreed timeframes</li>
            <li>Make payments according to the agreed schedule</li>
            <li>Ensure you have the rights to any materials you provide</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Revisions and Changes</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            The number of revisions included in your project will be specified in your project agreement. Additional revisions beyond the agreed scope may incur additional charges. Significant changes to the project scope may require a revised agreement and adjusted pricing.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Cancellation and Refunds</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Cancellation terms will be outlined in your project agreement. Generally:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--color-mist)] space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Deposits are non-refundable once work has begun</li>
            <li>If we cancel a project, you will receive a refund for work not yet completed</li>
            <li>Completed portions of work may be billed at our standard hourly rate</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Website Use</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
            When using our website, you agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--color-mist)] space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Use the website for any unlawful purpose</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the website</li>
            <li>Interfere with the proper functioning of the website</li>
            <li>Copy, reproduce, or distribute our content without permission</li>
            <li>Submit false or misleading information through our forms</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, Aloha Media Studio shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of our website or services. Our total liability for any claim shall not exceed the amount you paid for the specific service giving rise to the claim.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Disclaimer</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            Our website and services are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not guarantee that our website will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Indemnification</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Aloha Media Studio from any claims, damages, losses, or expenses arising from your use of our services, your violation of these terms, or your infringement of any third-party rights.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Idaho, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any disputes arising from these terms shall be resolved in the courts of Ada County, Idaho.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to this page. Your continued use of our website or services after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Severability</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            If any provision of these terms is found to be unenforceable, the remaining provisions will continue in full force and effect.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)] leading-relaxed">
            If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 p-6 bg-[var(--color-charcoal)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-graphite)]">
            <p class="text-[var(--color-cream)] font-semibold mb-2">Aloha Media Studio</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)]">Eagle, Idaho</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-mist)]">
              <a href="mailto:media@alohapublishing.com" class="text-[var(--color-coral)] hover:underline">media@alohapublishing.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--color-graphite)]">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[var(--color-mist)] hover:text-[var(--color-coral)] transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
          </svg>
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
